  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">SAMOS &#x2013; Supporting the Greek Government in Constructing a New Identification and Reception Centre in Samos (Phase II)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through this project, IOM provides essential support to the Government of Greece in their efforts to offer dignified living, shelter, hygiene and safety conditions and alleviate the suffering of the migrant population hosted in Samos. IOM proceeds with all necessary construction works for the creation of a new reception and identification centre in Samos, in a location identified and leased by the Greek authorities. Close coordination is ensured with the national authorities (Ministry of Citizen Protection, Ministry of Defence) and the local community.</narrative>
  </description>
